caption: Most people get this wrong, but perfecting your squat form is not just about aesthetics - it's about preventing injuries and maximizing workout effectiveness. Think about it: when you're squatting, you're putting your joints through a tremendous amount of stress. But what if I told you that by mastering the right form, you can reduce your risk of injury and get more out of your workout?
The Squat Mistake You've Been Making (And How to Fix It)
